(469, 88, '_leaders_repeater_2_leaders_name', 'field_5b0db71a1c939'),
(470, 88, 'leaders_repeater_2_leaders_description', 'Matt has been working in various engineering roles in the data warehousing and analytics space for the past 10 years. Prior to Starburst Data, Matt was Director of Engineering at Teradata leading engineering teams working on Presto. Matt was part of the team that led the initiative to bring open source, in particular Presto, to Teradata''s products. Prior to joining Teradata, Matt architected and led development efforts for the next generation distributed SQL engine at Hadapt which was acquired by Teradata in 2014.\r\nPrior to Hadapt, Matt was an early engineer at Vertica Systems which was acquired by HP (NYSE: HPQ). At Vertica Matt worked on the Query Optimizer.\r\nAt Starburst Data Matt is responsible for products, engineering, and customer support.'),
