(476, 88, 'leaders_repeater_3_leaders_description', 'Wojciech has a background of over 13 years of building products and running multiple engineering teams for various organisations and across different domains. At Starburst Data Wojciech is responsible for product development. Previously he was the Engineering Manager at the Teradata Center for Hadoop, running the Presto engineering operations in Warsaw, Poland. Prior to that, back in 2011, he built and ran the Polish engineering team, a subsidiary of Hadapt Inc., a pioneer in the SQL-on-Hadoop space. Hadapt was acquired by Teradata in 2014.\r\nEarlier, Wojciech built and lead teams on multi-year projects, from custom big e-commerce &amp; SCM platforms to PoS systems.\r\nWojciech holds a M.S. in Computer Science from the Wroclaw University of Technology.'),
