(3067, 340, 'presto_2c_1_presto_2c_content', 'Allow your business intelligence users and <strong>data scientists</strong> to use their favorite tools (Tableau, Qlik, Apache Superset) to access and analyze virtually any data source via Presto. Analyze data from HDFS, object stores, RDBMS (SQL Server, Oracle, MySQL, PostgreSQL), Kafka, Cassandra, MongoDB, and many others. Presto’s flexible architecture allows one perform analytics <strong>federated</strong> across multiple data sources at the same time. Easily combine historical data from <strong>HDFS</strong> or objects stores with most recent incoming data from <strong>Kafka</strong> in the same query.'),
