(3765, 346, 'page_blocks_0_block_content', 'With data volumes and types of data increasing on a daily basis, placing this data on a flexible storage medium such as HDFS or a cloud object storage such as Amazon''s S3, S3-compatible stores (Minio, ceph), and Azure''s Blob Storage provides a company with great flexibility on when and where they consume this data. Architected for separation of storage and compute, Presto can <span style="color: #253746;"><strong>scale up and down</strong></span> based on your analytics demand to access this data. There’s no need to move your data and provisioning compute to the exact need results in <span style="color: #253746;"><strong>significant cost savings.</strong></span>'),
