(4821, 356, 'page_blocks_2_content_rows_2_column_2_content', '<h3 class="light"><span style="color: #253746;">Deploy Anywhere</span></h3>\r\n<p class="small mb0" style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">The separation of storage and compute allows Presto flexible deployment options. Deploy on public clouds such as AWS and Azure, private clouds such as OpenStack, on premises on bare metal commodity hardware or in a virtualized environment. ware on premises. Or let us deploy and manage with our <b>fully managed Presto offering</b>.</span></p>'),
