(10779, 422, 'page_blocks_2_block_content', 'A solid architecture serves as the foundation of your enterprise query engine. Out of the box, Presto performs excellent for a majority of use cases but outside of the many tuning parameters under the hood, there are many more considerations to consider when deploying into a production environment. Items such as proper storage layout, connector tuning, split sizes, etc.. all need to be taken into consideration.\r\n\r\nLet the Presto experts guide you to achieve the best performance and maintainability in order to provide the end users with the best experience possible.'),
