(10801, 422, 'page_blocks_3_block_content', 'Given the proven power and capability of Presto for large-scale querying it is extremely important to be aware of a set of tuning consideration and best practices when implementing Presto into production. Out of the box, Presto has amazing performance capabilities but with any technology, it’s hard to know what users will throw at it.\r\n\r\nStarburst Data’s senior consultants can provide performance tuning and best practice engagements for any timeframe. From a few hours a week to full time engagements, let our Presto experts ensure your environment is running smoothly and at peak performance.'),
