(10823, 422, 'page_blocks_4_block_content', 'One of the unique features that makes Presto stand out from other query engines is the connector ecosystem. Connectors enable Presto to query data from a variety of different data sources. Some of these are relational databases, HDFS files, Object stores (S3, Azure) and NoSQL stores such as Cassandra.\r\n\r\nStarburst Data has created many certified connectors for Presto which uniquely qualifies us to create new connectors regardless of the data source. We’ve also taken open source connectors and made them “Enterprise Level” through performance testing, bug fixes and enhancements.'),
