(11961, 472, 'page_blocks_0_block_content', '<strong>Join us </strong>to learn and experience our energizing work environment.<img class="wp-image-454 alignright" src="http://starburstdata.dev.cc/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/starburst-data-culture-abstract.jpg" alt="" width="340" height="226" />\r\n\r\nAt Startburst Data we have an engineering-driven culture that fosters agile software development at its best. With self-organizing sub-teams and low-ceremony/high-efficiency development workflows. In our short and long term plans we feature a constant push for innovation, strive for technical excellence and state-of-the-art software engineering practices. Throughout our development cycles we adjust our approach by running continuous feedback and improvement loops.\r\n\r\nOur team features very strong software engineering talent, with years of core database engine and distributed systems development experience.\r\n\r\nStarburst Data has a healthy flat org structure that empowers engineers, lets them get out the best of them and grow. We have a very open communication culture and try to solve problems at their roots.\r\n\r\n<strong>Join us</strong> and bring your experiences, enthusiasm and ideas to the table. Let us teach you our ways, and we''ll gladly learn yours.'),
