(13678, 555, '_page_blocks_0_block_subtitle', 'field_5b197549268a6'),
(13679, 555, 'page_blocks_0_block_content', 'PrestoCare™ is a full-service offering that manages and administers your Presto infrastructure, reducing this time-consuming and distracting burden on your organization.\r\n\r\nOur highly experienced PrestoCare™ administrators and developers will leverage industry best practices to help optimize your Presto environment, while providing you with a new level of stability and performance. Whether is on-premises or on AWS or Azure, you can rest assure that the most qualified Presto experts providing an expert level of knowledge and care for your environment.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-553" src="http://starburstdata.dev.cc/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/presto-care-steps-1.png" alt="" width="1342" height="121" />\r\n\r\nStarburst Data can assist you with not only designing and building your Presto environment, we can take the administration and monitoring off your hands so you can focus on what you do best.'),
