(18287, 628, 'page_blocks_0_block_content', 'The Presto community consists of users, developers, and users who are also developers. Presto is used in production at very large scale at many well-known and well-respected companies. It works because many of the companies using Presto contribute back to the open source community improving it for everyone. This has made Presto very robust and and proven to scale to thousands of nodes, hundreds of petabytes, and hundreds of concurrent users performing analytical queries. This uniqueness continues to drive Presto as the best distributed SQL-on-Anything query engine.'),
